metadata.description: .painless is a digital glitch art collection that explores the concept of imperfection and the beauty that can arise from unexpected errors and malfunctions. The artworks in the .painless collection are all created using digital tools, but they are intentionally manipulated to create unexpected visual effects and glitches. The result is a collection of art that is both striking and thought-provoking, as it challenges our assumptions about what is "perfect" and what is "imperfect" in the digital world.
